  .medium-3.columns.text-center
    h3.gamma Rich Graphing
    p Fully-interactive, editable graphs. Multiple Y-axes, Logarithmic scales & options.

    h3.gamma Mixed Styling
    p Draw your graphs how you want. Mix lines, points and  bars. Mix stacked w/ isolated series.

    h3.gamma Themes
    p Ships with two themes. If you don’t like the default dark theme, switch to a light theme.


